{"word":"Circumcision","slug":"circumcision","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Circumcision</b> Institution of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=14'>Gen 17:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=12&verse=3'>Lev 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=22'>Joh 7:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=8'>Act 7:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=4&verse=11'>Rom 4:11</a><br/> A seal of righteousness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=2&verse=29'>Rom 2:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=4&verse=11'>Rom 4:11</a><br/> Performed on all males on the eighth day<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=13'>Gen 17:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=12&verse=3'>Lev 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=3&verse=5'>Phi 3:5</a><br/> Rite of, observed on the Sabbath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=23'>Joh 7:23</a><br/> A prerequisite of the privileges of the Passover<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=48'>Exo 12:48</a><br/> Child named at the time of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=4'>Gen 21:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=59'>Luk 1:59</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=21'>Luk 2:21</a><br/> Neglect of, punished<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=14'>Gen 17:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=24'>Exo 4:24</a><br/> Neglected<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=5&verse=7'>Jos 5:7</a><br/> Covenant promises of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=14'>Gen 17:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=8'>Act 7:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=3&verse=1'>Rom 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=4&verse=11'>Rom 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=9&verse=13'>Rom 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=5&verse=3'>Gal 5:3</a><br/> Necessity of, falsely taught by Judaizing Christians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=1'>Act 15:1</a><br/> Paul's argument against the continuance of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=2&verse=25'>Rom 2:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=2&verse=28'>Rom 2:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=6&verse=13'>Gal 6:13</a><br/> Characterized by Paul as a yoke<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=10'>Act 15:10</a><br/> Abrogated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=29'>Act 15:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=3&verse=30'>Rom 3:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=4&verse=11'>Rom 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=7&verse=19'>1Co 7:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=4'>Gal 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=5&verse=11'>Gal 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=6&verse=12'>Gal 6:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=2&verse=11'>Eph 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=2&verse=15'>Eph 2:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=2&verse=11'>Col 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=3&verse=11'>Col 3:11</a><br/> Instances of:<br/> - Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=27'>Gen 17:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=4'>Gen 21:4</a> <br/> - Shechemites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=34&verse=24'>Gen 34:24</a> <br/> - Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=25'>Exo 4:25</a> <br/> - Israelites at Gilgal<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=5&verse=9'>Jos 5:9</a> <br/> - John the Baptist<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=59'>Luk 1:59</a> <br/> - Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=21'>Luk 2:21</a> <br/> - Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=3&verse=5'>Phi 3:5</a> <br/> - Timothy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=3'>Act 16:3</a> <br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=12'>Exo 6:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=10&verse=16'>Deu 10:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=30&verse=6'>Deu 30:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=4&verse=4'>Jer 4:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=10'>Jer 6:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=9&verse=26'>Jer 9:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=2&verse=29'>Rom 2:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=15&verse=8'>Rom 15:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=3&verse=3'>Phi 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=2&verse=11'>Col 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=3&verse=11'>Col 3:11</a><br/> A designation of the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=45'>Act 10:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wor